org.apache.polygene.library.sql.generator.grammar.query

Class SetOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.polygene.library.sql.generator.grammar.query.SetOperation

  • public final class SetOperation
extends Object
    This enum represents the possible set operations to combine queries with. These set operations are UNION, INTERSECT, and EXCEPT.
